      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "Once again, the framing is focused around the subject's arm in a way that emphasizes the importance of the flower. However, the presence of the subject's shadow in the frame allows us to gain an understanding of what she looks like and how she is moving without her body itself being in the frame of the shot.",
