      ],
      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "This shot is framed around the subject's eye, a sharp change from previous shots that did not include the subjects face. The focus on the subject's eye makes the shot seem more personal as the framing around her hands and legs creates a sense of mystery and distance from the viewer. The eye never looks directly at the camera, creating a sense of intrusion on the subject.",
