      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "This shot is the first apearance of the subject's full face and upper body. This lends importance to the shot as it allows the audience to see her facial expressions for the first time, better communicating the emotions of the scene. She is framed directly in the center of the shot, appearing from the bottom. This makes her appearance feel more revealing.",
